<plot>For the first thirty years of his life Jean Touzet explored various artistic fields, being alternately an actor with Jean Vilar, a pianist, a conductor, etc. When he was offered to give life to the Cannes Festival, he dealt with all the administrative issues in an artistic way. It is most likely thanks to that that he succeeded in making the Cannes Festival an outstanding event, an "original creation".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?323089</url></doc>
